{"tid":734769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那製][有毒無害]【網上熱話】林超英憂扶手甩漆傳播有毒物質　港鐵：不會損害健康","createTime":"2018-07-09T02:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T05:34:20.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"af35b255c79987436aa588621b3be0767505313d","tid":734769,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180709/s00001/1531095837315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180709%2Fs00001%2F1531095837315&d=EhObDzPWrntWObDqJW3iFOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=b2331914\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180709%2Fs00001%2F1531095837315&h=f6c7ad20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180709/s00001/1531095837315</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180709/s00001/dc8e62f695c471cc79bfe5b54e0956d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180709%2Fs00001%2Fdc8e62f695c471cc79bfe5b54e0956d6.jpg&h=165ee4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180709/s00001/dc95c869c240e534919c6d1577cee95a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180709%2Fs00001%2Fdc95c869c240e534919c6d1577cee95a.jpg&h=1fd71dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車廂內，不時聽到廣播提醒乘客緊握扶手以保安全。不過前天文台長林超英日前於facebook發帖批評港鐵車廂扶手油漆磨損，憂慮會把有毒物質「贈送」乘客。港鐵回覆《明報》稱，車廂用料包括扶手油漆在內，「不會對人體健康構成損害」。<br />\n<br />\n林超英上周六（7日）上載一張港鐵車廂圖片，圖中原本黃色的扶手因油漆磨損，變成部分銀色。他於帖文中指出，扶手油漆磨損除了礙眼，更可能把有毒物質「贈送」給乘客，又稱有關情況已存在超過一年，要求港鐵盡快修補扶手，「不要破壞香港形象」。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引起網民關注。林超英向《明報》表示，扶手油漆剝落屬於非常明顯「甩漏」，加上興建鐵路時的錯漏，令市民對港鐵營運失去信心：「香港人是港鐵的真正大老闆，港鐵必須以香港總體利益為重，叫價不得過分，條件不可過苛，否則社會將大反彈。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港鐵回覆《明報》指，車廂用料包括扶手油漆在內，「不會對人體健康構成損害」，而港鐵收到車廂保養相關查詢後，會記錄並清潔及跟進。</strong><br />\n<br />\n林超英則說，「可能把有毒物質贈送給乘客」屬誇張表達手法，稱「有毒物質」借代油漆。他強調，帖文是想突顯港鐵「無鬼用」，無保好車廂保養，損害香港形象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">批支那車甩o左幾年，龜鐵都無補過油</span>"},{"pid":"b19a811d13e087996f516e77b070c2bb019fcaad","tid":734769,"uid":7206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"馬時亨做局長果時都係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府專養廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573ccbd0a533732588088a260ee558b76b8f8599","tid":734769,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04e2e58a012fb5f60fa66ceb52eb323bcdcb356","tid":734769,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"573ccbd0a533732588088a260ee558b76b8f8599","tid":734769,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"叫關公親口奶一支"},{"pid":"b032003796d1e3002a4f480e4cb1928b5bfbe8ac","tid":734769,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"657f1774d64f3158735727bfff1ec538fb3c47a0","tid":734769,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"雲海終於搵到接班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713a85b408b2f92747d234fda8828167850e8ca5","tid":734769,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"支那"},{"pid":"b8767e7b1d8cd2f8bd5409a8dec21ea9853848a7","tid":734769,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"呢批大陸車開左幾個月已經明顯脫色，都已經唔係新聞。"},{"pid":"6fabe4b44780734c6972174d721f9f3d52a7cb17","t